Language: <F P=105> Ukrainian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Sevastopol, 8 Jan -- Speaking on a Crimean radio 
program, Ivan Yermakov, head of the Sevastopol state 
administration, sharply criticized the leadership of Ukraine, 
saying that the Ukrainian Government's policy was leading to the 
impoverishment of the population, first of all, in Sevastopol. 
