<F P=102>  NC0801122894 Yerevan SNARK in English 1014 GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0801122894 </F>
<F P=104>  Yerevan SNARK </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Stepanakert, January 8 (SNARK)--The unexpected 
quietness exists at the Karabakh front from the last night. The 
military experts are of the opinion that quietness is caused by 
the new Azerbaijani detachments movements into the zone of 
military clashes. Meanwhile, Press-Service of the Defense Army 
told yesterday evening the Azerbaijani detachment managed to 
capture some frontiers and hills at the Iranian border. At the 
Martuni and Mardakert directions the Karabakh forces met 
success, Azeris had losses: 80 Azerbaijani soldiers and 
officers, 2 tanks and a military machine. 

