Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Defense Ministry press service provided the 
following information on 7 January. Despite sustaining crushing 
blows in various sectors of the front in recent days, the 
Armenian Armed Forces are not giving up their occupationist 
plans, and are trying to breach the defensive positions of the 
Azerbaijani Army. Their efforts in this direction are being 
brought to naught thanks to the gallantry of our fighters; and 
the enemy is retreating, while sustaining enormous losses. 
  Our brave fighters destroyed more than 200 enemy troops and 
more than 50 armored vehicles in fighting today. The fleeing 
Armenians, who were chased out of the positions they had 
previously occupied, are leaving behind considerable amounts of 
military hardware and provisions. The gallant Azerbaijani Army 
once again showed its strength to the enemy. 

