called on the Russian side to promote a peaceful settlement of 
the question of Azerbaijan's territorial integrity. Aliyev also 
asked for help in defending the 600,000-strong Azerbaijani 
community in Georgia, which is being subjected to attack by 
criminal elements. That was a report from the ANI news agency. 

