<H3> <TI>   Cabinet Cuts Military Spending By 20 Percent </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0801160794 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1045 GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0801160794 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>


