Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, 8 Jan -- IBERIA news agency has learned 
that the military expenditure has been cut by 20 percent and 
constitutes only 12 percent of the state budget for the year 
1994 prepared by the Georgian cabinet of ministers. 

