<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   `Unofficial' Talks With Ossetia End Successfully </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0801133494 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1045 GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0801133494 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, 8 Jan -- An IBERIA correspondent learned 
that Georgian-Ossetian negotiations held at an unofficial level 
in the North Ossetian capital of Vladikavkaz were successful. 
Several more rounds have been planned, after which, with 
Russia's mediation, official negotiations will start. 

