<F P=100> Georgia </F>
<H3> <TI>   Two Wounded as Hungry Crowd Storms Greens Office </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0801135094 Tbilisi IBERIA in Georgian 1045 GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0801135094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tbilisi IBERIA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Georgian </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Tbilisi, 8 Jan -- An IBERIA correspondent learned 
that during a distribution of a humanitarian aid in front of the 
office of the Georgian Greens party, in Mushtaidi Park in 
Tbilisi, a hungry, emaciated crowd of people stormed the office 
and plundered the humanitarian aid. 
  Two citizens suffered serious wounds and the owner of the 
humanitarian aid, (Kostas Papanastasiu) saved himself by running 
away. 

</TEXT>

