<H3> <TI>   Manned `Soyuz' Spacecraft Launched </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD0801102594 Moscow ITAR-TASS World Service in Russian 1011 
GMT 8 Jan 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0801102594 </F>
