<H3> <TI>   Soskovets Expected To Remain in Government </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  LD1101112094 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1059 GMT 11 Jan 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD1101112094 </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow ITAR-TASS </F>


